00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:04,040
which means reflection of space,

596
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:06,040
left hand into right hand,

597
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:09,040
is not a good symmetry of nature.

598
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:12,040
It's an ancient fact from the 50s

599
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:15,040
that it was discovered that the reflection,

600
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:17,040
the mirror reflection of a process,

601
00:25:17,040 --> 00:25:20,040
is not another possible process.

602
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:22,040
Now, in quantum electrodynamics,

603
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:24,040
the mirror image of any process

604
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:26,040
is another possible process.

605
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:28,040
That itself is a symmetry.

606
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:30,040
It's not a continuous symmetry.

607
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:32,040
It's a discrete symmetry.

608
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:34,040
You take everything and you reflect it.

609
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:36,040
You don't rotate it. You reflect it.

610
00:25:36,040 --> 00:25:38,040
You take the left hand and the right hand.

611
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:41,040
There's no hand which is sort of midway...

612
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:43,040
There's no continuous way to go

613
00:25:43,040 --> 00:25:45,040
from left hand to right hand.

614
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:48,040
So replacing every left hand by a right hand

615
00:25:48,040 --> 00:25:51,040
or every left screw thread

616
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:53,040
with a right screw thread and so forth,

617
00:25:53,040 --> 00:25:55,040
that's a symmetry of quantum electrodynamics.

618
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:59,040
And it's also a symmetry of quantum chromodynamics.

619
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:02,040
It is not a symmetry of the weak interactions.

