00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:40,040
So there are two kinds of electrons,

653
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:44,040
right-handed and left-handed.

654
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:49,040
Now, what happens in a beta decay like this?

